Ampun, tuanku!

84
00:03:23,250 --> 00:03:24,410
Tuanku jangan murka.

85
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:25,730
Tuanku.

86
00:03:25,970 --> 00:03:27,240
Jangan menyakiti tubuh tuanku.

87
00:03:28,780 --> 00:03:29,820
(Istana Ci'an)

88
00:03:29,820 --> 00:03:30,440
Tuanku maharani,

89
00:03:31,370 --> 00:03:34,260
khabarnya maharaja memanggil
jeneral mengadap baginda hari ini.

90
00:03:34,780 --> 00:03:36,080
Baginda buat susunan pasukan tentera.

91
00:03:36,850 --> 00:03:40,340
Rasanya mereka telah
menggunakan maklumat tersebut.

92
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,450
Asalnya,

93
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:44,410
beta berharap boleh dapat

94
00:03:44,690 --> 00:03:45,990
berita baik daripada Gundik Rong.

95
00:03:46,790 --> 00:03:47,680
Tak sangka

96
00:03:48,020 --> 00:03:49,350
dia bukan saja tak berguna,

97
00:03:49,690 --> 00:03:51,950
malah bergaduh dengan Qin Yu semalam.

98
00:03:53,890 --> 00:03:54,660
Tuanku maharani,

99
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:56,150
patik dapat maklumat tadi.

100
00:03:56,690 --> 00:03:58,970
Pagi ini, baginda pergi
ke istana Gundik Rong

101
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:01,210
untuk makan sarapan bersama Gundik Rong.

102
00:04:01,210 --> 00:04:02,390
Tak sangka ada perkara begitu.

103
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:06,210
(Maharani balu sebagai juara dalam
perbalahan dalam istana sebelum ini)

104
00:04:06,210 --> 00:04:07,240
(memang disanjung dengan kehebatannya.)

105
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,790
(Dia lebih licik daripada musang.)

106
00:04:08,890 --> 00:04:10,260
(Orang yang tak berguna untuk dia)

107
00:04:10,260 --> 00:04:11,570
(akan dibuang begitu saja.)

108
00:04:11,950 --> 00:04:13,610
(Namun jika seseorang itu
masih berguna untuk dia,)

109
00:04:13,730 --> 00:04:15,650
(dia pasti akan
mempergunakannya sehabisnya!)

110
00:04:16,460 --> 00:04:18,630
(Ini salah Qin Yu itu sebab
rosakkan rancangan saya.)

111
00:04:18,810 --> 00:04:20,610
(Bagaimana jika maharani balu
rasa saya masih berguna)

112
00:04:20,610 --> 00:04:21,650
(dan berubah fikiran?)

113
00:04:21,650 --> 00:04:23,200
(Saya tak boleh tunggu di sini saja.)

114
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:24,980
Fu Ling,

115
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:26,890
tolong saya sediakan barang.

116
00:04:27,900 --> 00:04:30,030
Patik, Yan Yiyi,
memberi salam kepada tuanku maharani.

117
00:04:30,140 --> 00:04:31,480
Kenapa awak berlutut pula?

118
00:04:32,180 --> 00:04:33,250
Cepat bangun dan duduk di sini.

119
00:04:34,380 --> 00:04:34,740
Patik tak berani.

120
00:04:37,060 --> 00:04:37,540
Kenapa?

121
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:40,670
Patik gagal sempurnakan
misi yang diberi tuanku maharani.

122
00:04:40,770 --> 00:04:42,080
Patik rasa bersalah

123
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:43,170
dan sudi dihukum.

124
00:04:43,460 --> 00:04:45,570
Sila hantar patik ke istana dingin.

125
00:04:45,570 --> 00:04:47,020
Patik sudi terimanya.

126
00:04:48,020 --> 00:04:49,320
Beta sangka apa yang berlaku,

127
00:04:49,930 --> 00:04:52,060
rupa-rupanya kerana perkara remeh ini.

128
00:04:52,470 --> 00:04:54,210
Awak setia pada beta

129
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:56,150
dan ada pertalian darah dengan beta,

130
00:04:56,940 --> 00:04:59,970
beta tak sampai hati
usir awak ke istana dingin.

131
00:05:02,530 --> 00:05:03,300
Bangunlah.

132
00:05:04,490 --> 00:05:06,770
(Kata-katanya sedap didengar,
ternyata dia mahu berubah fikiran.)

133
00:05:08,530 --> 00:05:09,680
Patik junjung kasih tuanku maharani.

134
00:05:13,490 --> 00:05:14,680
Khabarnya, maharaja

135
00:05:15,380 --> 00:05:17,800
pergi ke istana awak semalam

136
00:05:18,230 --> 00:05:19,560
dan makan sarapan bersama awak.

137
00:05:20,030 --> 00:05:21,000
Betulkah?

138
00:05:23,110 --> 00:05:23,680
Ya.

139
00:05:25,820 --> 00:05:28,770
Biasanya maharaja sibuk
dengan urusan pentadbiran.

140
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,750
Baginda jarang
ambil peduli tentang harem.

141
00:05:31,860 --> 00:05:32,750
Sekarang,

142
00:05:33,170 --> 00:05:35,530
baginda ambil berat akan awak.

143
00:05:36,110 --> 00:05:38,630
Kelak, awak berada di sisi baginda

144
00:05:39,020 --> 00:05:42,130
dan dapatkan maklumat untuk beta.

145
00:05:42,550 --> 00:05:46,390
Jika awak terdengar perkara
yang berkaitan dengan maharaja,

146
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:48,820
laporkanlah kepada beta.

147
00:05:49,190 --> 00:05:50,330
(Si musang licik.)

148
00:05:50,330 --> 00:05:51,910
(Saya dah agak
awak ada rancangan jahat.)

149
00:05:54,670 --> 00:05:55,520
Tuanku maharani,

150
00:05:55,900 --> 00:05:58,800
patik tak mampu lakukannya.

151
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,840
Awak tak mampu?

152
00:06:02,490 --> 00:06:04,340
Maksudnya, tuanku maharani mahu

153
00:06:04,340 --> 00:06:07,100
patik menjadi pengintip
di sisi maharaja?

154
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:09,700
Namun baginda ikhlas terhadap patik.

155
00:06:09,700 --> 00:06:11,610
Patik berasal dari keluarga jeneral,

156
00:06:11,610 --> 00:06:13,460
namun patik tahu mengenang budi.

157
00:06:13,860 --> 00:06:16,680
Patik takkan mengkhianati maharaja.

158
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:18,840
Maksud awak ialah

159
00:06:19,650 --> 00:06:21,640
awak sanggup mengingkari arahan beta

160
00:06:22,180 --> 00:06:23,660
demi melindungi maharaja?

161
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:28,710
Sila tarik balik titah tuanku maharani.

162
00:06:30,420 --> 00:06:33,040
Awak benar-benar sangka
beta tak berani menghukum awak?

163
00:06:34,660 --> 00:06:35,460
Patik sanggup dihukum

164
00:06:35,610 --> 00:06:37,070
demi maharaja.

165
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:38,400
Baik.

166
00:06:39,430 --> 00:06:40,740
Gundik Rong,

167
00:06:41,060 --> 00:06:43,130
awak bersikap biadab dan berniat jahat.

168
00:06:43,380 --> 00:06:46,310
Awak akan dijatuhi 30 sebatan,
kemudian diusir ke istana dingin.

